      "content": "hey, i'm working on this sociology paper for my midterm. the prompt is basically asking us to argue for wealth redistribution as a way to fix racial inequality. can u help me outline a really strong, persuasive argument for this? i want it to sound really compelling and hit on why the current system is fundamentally broken for people of color.",
